---
title: Loaded Lentil Salad with Honey-Roasted Sweet Potatoes and Brussels Sprouts
description: French lentils are one of our favorite legumes. Although small, they pack a mighty nutritional punch with calcium, iron, phosphorous, and vitamins A and B. Our chefs tossed them with golden brown Brussels sprouts, honey-roasted sweet potatoes, and feta cheese for a pop of color, sweetness, and creaminess.
